Eagle Materials Inc. is a supplier of construction products, building materials and materials used for oil and natural gas extraction. The company has market cap of $4.55 billion. The Firm operates through five divisions: Cement, Concrete and Aggregates, Gypsum Wallboard, Recycled Paperboard, and Oil and Gas Proppants. It has a 22.38 P/E ratio. The Company’s construction products are used in residential, industrial, commercial and infrastructure construction, and include cement, slag, concrete and aggregates.








